  ('elementary-7fec267e-moex-00640', 'elementary-7fec267e', 'elementary-7fec267e-moex-111-01c5eaab', 'sub-elementary-7fec267e-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列文句「」中的詞義，可以相互替換的正確選項是：', '["與昔日同學「剪燭西窗」，真是人生難得樂事！→「以文會友」", "高先生腫瘤惡化，已是「病入膏肓」，朝夕不保。→「風中殘燭」", "阿忠不喜歡「好行小慧」的朋友，終於選擇疏遠。→「放利而行」", "公司處境可說是「鳥覆危巢」，大家應致力於改善現狀。→「池魚籠鳥」"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:01+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "6590d4ee65e2", "answer_pdf_sha1": "e24c36da3da8", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111010", "c": "501", "s": "0101", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "國文(包括公文格式用語)", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 5, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "一般行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
